<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Lemon73 Blog</title><link>https://lemon73-computing.github.io/blog/en/</link><description>Recent content on Lemon73 Blog</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>en</language><lastBuildDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 21:20:00 +0900</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://lemon73-computing.github.io/blog/en/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Release Schedule: Alice Novel v0.9.3</title><link>https://lemon73-computing.github.io/blog/en/p/20241004-alicenovel-next/</link><pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 21:20:00 +0900</pubDate><guid>https://lemon73-computing.github.io/blog/en/p/20241004-alicenovel-next/</guid><description>&lt;p>I am planning to release next version, v0.9.3 of Alice Novel. That&amp;rsquo;s include some CI/CD fixes, changing directory structured and dependencies update.&lt;/p>
&lt;h3 id="currently">Currently
&lt;/h3>&lt;p>Currently, I decided to include some PRs, it shows below.&lt;/p>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>docs (license): change the license (&lt;a class="link" href="https://github.com/AliceNovel/AliceNovel/pull/72" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>#72&lt;/a>)&lt;/li>
&lt;li>chore (dependencies): bump dependencies (&lt;a class="link" href="https://github.com/AliceNovel/AliceNovel/pull/73" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>#73&lt;/a>)&lt;/li>
&lt;li>chore (dependencies): bump maui version (&lt;a class="link" href="https://github.com/AliceNovel/AliceNovel/pull/74" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>#74&lt;/a>)&lt;/li>
&lt;li>chore (ci/cd): recreate the android ci/cd on azure devops (&lt;a class="link" href="https://github.com/AliceNovel/AliceNovel/pull/77" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>#77&lt;/a>)&lt;/li>
&lt;li>build (deps): bump packages (&lt;a class="link" href="https://github.com/AliceNovel/AliceNovel/pull/78" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>#78&lt;/a>)&lt;/li>
&lt;li>chore (ci/cd): bump actions/upload-artifact from v3 to v4 (&lt;a class="link" href="https://github.com/AliceNovel/AliceNovel/pull/46" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>#46&lt;/a>)&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;h3 id="schedule">Schedule
&lt;/h3>&lt;p>I want to add some PRs by next release.&lt;/p>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>chore (scripts): move scripts files and update documentations (&lt;a class="link" href="https://github.com/AliceNovel/AliceNovel/pull/76" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>#76&lt;/a>)&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;p>And, this application has issue about its save system. So the system has bugs and it need to replace into new system. (Related: &lt;a class="link" href="https://github.com/AliceNovel/AliceNovel/issues/67" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>#67&lt;/a>)&lt;/p>
&lt;p>In addition, I think that &lt;a class="link" href="https://github.com/AliceNovel/AliceNovel/issues/69" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>#69&lt;/a> (disable the save button until read &lt;code>.anproj&lt;/code> file) and &lt;a class="link" href="https://github.com/AliceNovel/AliceNovel/issues/10" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>#10&lt;/a> (i18n English) is easy to close issue.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>In short, I have a view to fix &lt;a class="link" href="https://github.com/AliceNovel/AliceNovel/pull/76" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>#76&lt;/a>, &lt;a class="link" href="https://github.com/AliceNovel/AliceNovel/pull/67" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>#67&lt;/a> (include &lt;a class="link" href="https://github.com/AliceNovel/AliceNovel/issues/61" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>#61&lt;/a> for Android and &lt;a class="link" href="https://github.com/AliceNovel/AliceNovel/issues/47" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>#47&lt;/a> for Windows), &lt;a class="link" href="https://github.com/AliceNovel/AliceNovel/pull/69" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>#69&lt;/a>, &lt;a class="link" href="https://github.com/AliceNovel/AliceNovel/pull/10" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>#10&lt;/a> and some refactoring by the release of v0.9.3.&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="distribute">Distribute
&lt;/h2>&lt;ul>
&lt;li>&lt;a class="link" href="./" >Lemon73 Blog (here)&lt;/a> (EN: October 04, 2024 / JP: October 05, 2024)&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul></description></item><item><title>Archives</title><link>https://lemon73-computing.github.io/blog/en/archives/</link><pubDate>Tue, 20 Feb 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://lemon73-computing.github.io/blog/en/archives/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Links</title><link>https://lemon73-computing.github.io/blog/en/links/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://lemon73-computing.github.io/blog/en/links/</guid><description>&lt;p>To use this feature, add &lt;code>links&lt;/code> section to frontmatter.&lt;/p>
